# Routines

Scheduled routines that execute prompts on Claude Code automatically.

## Maintenance routines (shipped with the bot)

- [[update-check]] — Checks daily for Claude Code or repo updates
- [[journal-audit]] — Nightly audit that checks all agents' journals for completeness and fills gaps
- [[vault-graph-update]] — Regenerates the vault knowledge graph daily at 4am

## Your routines

Add your own scheduled routines here as you create them. Use the `/routine` command in Telegram to launch the interactive `create-routine` skill, or create `.md` files directly in this folder.

Example entry format:
```
- [[my-routine]] — Short description of what it does and when it runs
```
